May 30 1998 , Afghanistan-Tajikistan Border Region, M 6.6
At least 4,000 people killed, many thousands injured and homeless in Badakhshan and Takhar Provinces, Afghanistan . Felt strongly at Mazar-e Sharif , Afghanistan. Felt at Kabul , Afghanistan. Felt at Andijon and Samarqand ; at Toshkent , Uzbekistan . Also felt at Islamabad , Peshawar and Rawalpindi , Pakistan and Dushanbe , Tajikistan .
